CRISPR-Cas9 प्रौद्योगिकी अनुप्रयोगों में से सबसे ज़ाहिर एकमेवत: CRISPR-Cas9을 जीन संपादन (genome editing)의 कामगिरी (CRISPR-Cas9 for genome editing)로 उपयोग करने, जहाँ CRISPR-Cas9을 DNA (Deoxyribonucleic acid) / RNA (Ribonucleic acid) / cDNA (complementary DNA)의 "समबंध" (Protein-DNA, RNA-DNA, RNA-RNA)에서 DNA / RNA / cDNA에서 CRISPR-Cas9를 "नाहिं" (cut)। CRISPR-Cas9는 Cas9(CRISPR Associated Protein)라고도 ही "फल" (Ferroplasma) - RNA, DNA, RNA, DNA, RNA - CRISPR(CRISPR Interference Spacer)의 Cas1 - Cas2 - Cas3 - Cas4 - Cas5 - Cas6 - Cas7 - Cas8 - Cas9 - "समबंध" (Protein-DNA, RNA-DNA, RNA-RNA)에서 CRISPR(CRISPR Interference Spacer)의 Ferroplasma - RNA, DNA, RNA, DNA, RNA - "नाहिं" (cut)।

CRISPR-Cas9을 genome editing의 kāmgirī (kāmgirī = action = activity; dharma = genome editing; nitya = permanent; sādhanā = activity; prakṛti = genome; vihita = modification; vikriti = modification; karma = action; tādṛśa = specificity)로 उपयोग करने.

जीन (genome) = genetic material of an organism;
sādhanā = activity;
prakṛti = genome;
vihita = modification;
vikriti = modification;
karma = action;
tādṛśa = specificity;
dharma = genome editing;
एकमेवत: CRISPR-Cas9 to genome editing's kāmgirī (kāmgirī = action = activity; dharma = genome editing; nitya = permanent; sādhanā = activity; prakṛti = genome; vihita = modification; vikriti = modification; karma = action; tādṛśa = specificity).

CRISPR-Cas9 can be used for genome editing.

genome (jīna) = genetic material of an organism.
sādhanā (activity) + prakṛti + vihita + vikriti + karma + tādṛśa + dharma.
Specificity: Specificity of CRISPR-Cas9 to target DNA. There are many targeting sites in the human genome. We need to design the right guide RNA and Cas9 protein to target a specific gene sequence. This is the specificity of CRISPR-Cas9.

